{"tid":1960361,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"柒婆求財 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-04-06T06:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T07:08:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f222aed9aa9520819ed91100c641988e231fb506","tid":1960361,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200406/20894453/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200406%2F20894453%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLfSletu%2BpyBbwtETYsduqsw%3D&h=69b71223\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200406%2F20894453%2F&h=016e9e3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200406/20894453/</a><br />\n<br />\n柒婆求財 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200406/large/1586072160_7374.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200406%2Flarge%2F1586072160_7374.jpg&h=a5dc87cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一個問題，香港絕大多數人想來想去想不明白，在香港出生、長大，受盡香港恩惠的柒婆，究竟是為了甚麼，竟如此出賣香港，從法律、制度上徹底摧毀香港，剝奪香港人的人權、自由，破壞香港的價值觀，葬送香港人的希望。<br />\n<br />\n是甚麼，可以令一個人全無尊嚴，在全世界眾目睽睽之下出爾反爾，不顧誠信，在一片驅趕聲中賴死唔走？<br />\n<br />\n沒想到，答案居然是求財，是為了錢。<br />\n<br />\n不信？政府公佈2020至2021年度特首林鄭薪酬預算開支為521萬港幣，逆巿加薪12萬。武漢肺炎肆虐，遲遲不封關、導致社區傳播，令香港各行各業面對前所未有的困局，小企業一間一間執笠，許多人失業、減薪或停薪，林鄭及其問責班子不但不需問責，亦不與巿民共度時艱，竟然逆巿加薪。世上竟有這樣不負責任的從政者。為了錢，不顧顏面，亦全無政治智慧。<br />\n<br />\n不如看看全球各地高官在疫情下收入有無變化，馬來西亞全體內閣減薪兩個月，新加坡全體內閣減薪三個月，南韓副部級以上官員減薪三成，肯亞總統減薪八成&hellip;&hellip;只有香港，成事不足、敗事有餘、不柒不做的特首，在香港人最艱困的時刻，每年打劫庫房多12萬。要貪錢到何等地步才能做得出來？<br />\n<br />\n你求財啫！一早開口，相信全香港超過九成人願意夾錢送你走，500萬人，每人夾100元，都有5億港幣。何必搞死香港？ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"a58cff094d58d1061f09be2c4af1d619ef4ed082","tid":1960361,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"不一定是錢<br />\n牠喜歡威 牠喜歡考第一<br />\n牠喜歡高高在上的地位<br />\n權力令牠高潮 一發不可收拾"},{"pid":"c03c8e2673a0fa546682e6e16389be2742a42990","tid":1960361,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T06:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2623dc4ea6c05b4d443f596af7f8dfac868d0f39","tid":1960361,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}